==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tilley seed
<hw>Til"ley seed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The
seeds of a small tree (<spn>Croton Pavana</spn>) common in the Malay
Archipelago. These seeds furnish croton oil, like those of <spn>Croton
Tiglium</spn>.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>tilly</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tillman</ent>⟦br⟧
